Class RationaleStatus

java.lang.Object
  edu.wpi.cs.jburge.SEURAT.rationaleData.RationaleStatus

public class RationaleStatus
extends java.lang.Object

Defines the contents of a RationaleStatus record. These capture errors and warnings discovered in the rationale.
